{"_id":"191aacaecaa92ce1","name":"Logic Upgrade: Self-Defense","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"Grant yourself +2 to the Defense of your choice for 1 round.","prerequisite":"Droid","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide","page":27,"tags":["defense","feat","general","knowledge","survivability","utility"],"bonus_feat_for":[],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":{"value":"Grant yourself +2 to the Defense of your choice for 1 round."},"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"attack","value":0,"type":"untyped","predicates":[],"enabled":false,"priority":500,"description":"[REQUIRES MANUAL MAPPING] Logic Upgrade: Self-Defense"}]},"shortSummary":"Grant yourself +2 to the Defense of your choice for 1 round."},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.379Z","detectedPredicates":[],"id":"swse.feat.logic_upgrade_self_defense"}}}
{"_id":"192923f60db38831","name":"Staggering Attack","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/upgrade.svg","system":{"featType":"general","benefit":"When using a melee weapon with which you are proficient, you can make an attack that disrupts an enemy's concentration. You take a -2 penalty on your attack roll, and if your attack deals damage, the target takes a -2 penalty to Skill Checks until the end of your next turn. Alternatively, you can take a -5 penalty to your attack roll, and if your attack deals damage, the target takes a -5 penalty to Skill Checks until end of your next turn.","prerequisite":"Base Attack Bonus +1","special":"","normalText":"","sourcebook":"Galaxy at War","page":27,"tags":["control","feat","general","offense"],"bonus_feat_for":["f62ca2e639cab614"],"uses":{"current":0,"max":0,"perDay":false},"costNumeric":null,"description":{"value":"<div class=\"swse-feat-description\">\n<p><strong>Reference Book:</strong> Star Wars Saga Edition Galaxy at War</p>\n<p><strong>Source:</strong> https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Staggering_Attack_(GaW)</p>\n<p>You can deliver punishing blows to your enemies, distracting them and keeping them from focusing their efforts.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Base Attack Bonus +1</p>\n<h4>Effect</h4>\n<p>When using a melee weapon with which you are proficient, you can make an attack that disrupts an enemy&#x27;s concentration. You take a -2 penalty on your attack roll, and if your attack deals damage, the target takes a -2 penalty to Skill Checks until the end of your next turn. Alternatively, you can take a -5 penalty to your attack roll, and if your attack deals damage, the target takes a -5 penalty to Skill Checks until end of your next turn.</p>\n</div>"},"executionModel":"PASSIVE","subType":"STATE","abilityMeta":{"modifiers":[{"target":"attack","value":2,"type":"untyped","predicates":["attack.when-hit","attack.with-melee","turn.once-per-round"],"enabled":true,"priority":500,"description":"Staggering Attack"}]},"shortSummary":"Impose penalties to enemy Skill Checks with a successful attack.","prerequisitesText":"Base Attack Bonus +1","referenceBooks":["Star Wars Saga Edition Galaxy at War"],"sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Staggering_Attack_(GaW)"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"migratedToState":true,"migrationDate":"2026-03-08T18:22:17.379Z","detectedPredicates":["attack.when-hit","attack.with-melee","turn.once-per-round"],"id":"swse.feat.staggering_attack","featContentRefresh":{"source":"swse_feats.json","sourceUrl":"https://swse.fandom.com/wiki/Staggering_Attack_(GaW)","updatedFields":["system.description.value","system.benefit","system.prerequisite","system.special","system.normalText","system.shortSummary"]}}}}
